            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Flavi<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ae</supplied> C<supplied reason="lost">res</supplied>centiae frater et soror <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Crescentius qui et Valentianus <lb n="3"/>vixit annos IIII me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>ses</abbr></expan> XI dies XI <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>dep</abbr><ex>ositus</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Iulias et Anastasia qui <note>sic</note> et <lb n="5"/>Verula vixit me<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>ses</abbr></expan> XI dies VIII <expan><abbr>dep</abbr><ex>osita</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Au<lb break="no" n="6"/>gustas
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschrift auf der Sarkophagvorderseite innerhalb einer tabula ansata. Maßangaben ohne Deckel. Christusmonogramm innerhalb der rechten ansa.</p>
            </div>
